modules.description: This module implements a monadic interface for handling HTTP requests and responses using Cohttp. It provides functions for creating and composing IO actions, including `return`, `map`, `bind`, and `fail`, along with HTTP methods `get`, `post`, `put`, and `delete` for interacting with web services. These operations work with strings for request bodies and responses, and take headers as key-value lists, making them suitable for RESTful API interactions.
